<h1>Prudential Norms (PNR13&#8211;18) &#8212; Visualization Guide</h1>

<p class="meta"><b>Department:</b> Microfinance Supervision Department (MFSD)</p>
<p class="meta"><b>Regulatory Reference:</b> Regulation No 60/2023 of 27/03/2023, Articles 16 &amp; 20</p>
<p class="meta"><b>Data Source:</b> VISION Oracle EDW &#8212; <code>Prudential_norms_consolidated.sql</code></p>
<p class="meta"><b>Date:</b> February 2026</p>

<hr>

<h2>Overview</h2>

<p>This document provides visualization recommendations for the six Other Prudential Norms (PNR13&#8211;PNR18) monitored for Deposit-Taking Microfinance Institutions (DTMFIs). Each norm has a regulatory threshold that institutions must not exceed.</p>

<h3>Summary of Norms</h3>

<table>
  <tr><th>PNR</th><th>Indicator</th><th>Denominator</th><th>Threshold</th><th>Applies To</th></tr>
  <tr><td>PNR13</td><td>Investment in Fixed Assets</td><td>Core Capital</td><td>Max 50%</td><td>MF, DSACCO, USACCO, OSACCO</td></tr>
  <tr><td>PNR14</td><td>Land &amp; Buildings</td><td>Total Assets</td><td>Max 5%</td><td>MF, DSACCO, USACCO, OSACCO</td></tr>
  <tr><td>PNR15</td><td>Non-Earning Assets</td><td>Total Assets</td><td>Max 10%</td><td>MF, DSACCO, USACCO, OSACCO</td></tr>
  <tr><td>PNR16</td><td>Borrowing Ratio</td><td>Total Assets</td><td>Max 25%</td><td>MF, DSACCO, USACCO, OSACCO</td></tr>
  <tr><td>PNR17</td><td>Placement Limits</td><td>Core Capital</td><td>Max 25%</td><td>MF, DSACCO, USACCO, OSACCO</td></tr>
  <tr><td>PNR18</td><td>Investment in Equity Shares</td><td>Core Capital</td><td>Max 25%</td><td>MF, DSACCO, USACCO, OSACCO</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Data Available from Consolidated Query</h3>

<p>The <code>Prudential_norms_consolidated.sql</code> query returns one row per institution per month with:</p>

<table>
  <tr><th>Column</th><th>Description</th></tr>
  <tr><td>LE_Book</td><td>Institution code</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Year_Month</td><td>Reporting period (YYYYMM)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>CATEGORY_TYPE</td><td>MF, SACCO, OSACCO, or DSACCO</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Stakeholder_Name</td><td>Institution name</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Investment_In_Fixed_Assets</td><td>PNR13 numerator</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Land_And_Buildings</td><td>PNR14 numerator</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Non_Earning_Assets</td><td>PNR15 numerator</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Borrowings</td><td>PNR16 numerator</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Placement_Limits</td><td>PNR17 numerator</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Investment_In_Equity_Shares</td><td>PNR18 numerator</td></tr>
</table>

<p><b>Note:</b> Ratios must be computed in Power BI by joining with CAR data (core capital) and total assets from the Capital Adequacy queries.</p>

<hr>

<h2>Recommended DAX Measures</h2>

<p>These measures should be created in Power BI after joining the consolidated query with the CAR dataset:</p>

<pre>
PNR13 Ratio = DIVIDE([Investment_In_Fixed_Assets], [Core_Capital], 0) * 100
PNR14 Ratio = DIVIDE([Land_And_Buildings], [Total_Assets], 0) * 100
PNR15 Ratio = DIVIDE([Non_Earning_Assets], [Total_Assets], 0) * 100
PNR16 Ratio = DIVIDE([Borrowings], [Total_Assets], 0) * 100
PNR17 Ratio = DIVIDE([Placement_Limits], [Core_Capital], 0) * 100
PNR18 Ratio = DIVIDE([Investment_In_Equity_Shares], [Core_Capital], 0) * 100
</pre>

<p>Conditional formatting measure (reusable pattern):</p>

<pre>
PNR13 Status =
    SWITCH(
        TRUE(),
        [PNR13 Ratio] > 50, "Breach",
        [PNR13 Ratio] > 40, "Warning",
        "Compliant"
    )
</pre>

